 Elias","date":"August 8, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Muslim women, do not look down on any gift for your neighbor, even a sheep's hoof.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6017, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1030 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":586,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/02\/27\/be-kind-to-neighbors\/","url_meta":{"origin":7744,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Neighbors: Be kind to neighbors, regardless of religion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 27, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Mujahid reported: We were with Abdullah ibn Amr while his servant prepared to distribute a sheep. Abdullah said, \u201cYoung man, when you are finished, then begin with our Jewish neighbor.\u201d A man said, \u201cJewish? May Allah correct you!\u201d Abdullah said, \u201cI heard the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32921,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/27\/gabriel-emphasizes-neighbors\/","url_meta":{"origin":7744,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Neighbors: Gabriel emphasizes good behavior to neighbors","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2019","fo